#: ../../language/error_codes/E0029.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `unused_package`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0029.md:5
msgid ""
"This warning is emitted when a package is listed as an import but no code"
" in the current package refers to it. Remove the import if it was left "
"over from a refactor, or use the package through its alias if the "
"dependency is still needed."
msgstr ""
"当某个包被列为导入项，但当前包中没有任何代码引用它时，会发出此警告。如果该导入是重构后遗留的，请移除它；如果仍然需要该依赖，请通过其别名使用该包。"

